Package: tabviz
Title: Interactive Tables with Embedded Visualizations
Version: 0.37.0
Authors@R:
    person("Antoine", "Baldassari", , "baldassarian@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Antoine Baldassari [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Antoine Baldassari <baldassarian@gmail.com>
Description: Create interactive tables with embedded visualizations including
    forest plots, sparklines, bar charts, and more. Ideal for meta-analysis,
    regression results, dashboards, and data reports. Rendered using modern web
    technologies (Svelte, D3.js) for R Markdown, Quarto, Shiny, and standalone
    HTML. Features include collapsible groups, 17 column types, conditional
    styling, publication-ready themes, and static export to SVG/PDF/PNG/PPTx.
    A companion JavaScript package <https://www.npmjs.com/package/@tabviz/core>
    provides the same runtime and authoring API for direct use from web applications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
